00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:43.000
Sou o Sr. Michael Bangoora, filho do saudoso Sr. Tiamu Bangoora...

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:44.000
(Risos)

00:02:44.000 --> 00:02:46.000
